title: Top New Hampshire Republicans tell Christie to keep going
text:
> Top News Top New Hampshire Republicans tell Christie to keep going In this Oct. 7, 2015 photo, Republican presidential candidate Gov. Chris Christie, R-N.J., talks with employees during a campaign stop at East Coast Lumber in East Hampstead, N.H. Despite single-digit poll numbers, New Hampshire Republicans tell Chris Christie: Keep going. (AP Photo/Jim Cole) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
